data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION!  This beautiful well-kept home is nestled in the sought-out Barrington Estates neighborhood!! Sitting on a corner lot, this 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom features hardwood floors, open floor plan, separate living and dining room and an upgraded spacious eat-in kitchen. On the second floor, you'll find your owners suite with separate shower/tub and walk-in closet, two secondary bedrooms and an oversized loft area, which makes for a perfect kids playroom/ office or media room. This community offers swim/tennis amenities and walking distance to Gary Pirkle Park and in the award-winning Gwinnett School District. Convenient to highway access, shopping and recreation such as Lake Lanier, the Mall of Georgia, Historic Downtown Buford, and Suwanee Town Center.
